parameters:
Prince Rex: You all made a bad bet! You are inferior to
Caron in terms of military strength, wealth, and power... in
all aspects.
Prince Rex: You all bet against me!
Prince Rex: But behold this azure sky!

Prince Rex: When the storm subsides, everything will be in
my hands! You brave heroes! The gold and silver treasures
stored in the royal palace!
Prince Rex: The throne awaits the rightful one!

Prince Rex: The wicked Caron will disappear, and the old era
will come to an end. From now on, together with all of you,
we will build a new era!

Prince Rex: I will always be a king who goes to the
battlefield! That is the true form of the rightful king of
the Fotizona Empire!

Prince Rex: Under the rule of the rightful king, the empire
will regain justice and order.
King Rex: I will now announce my first order as the king.

Prince Rex: Raise the flag! Raise the sword! Raise the
spear!

King Rex: Let our complete victory resound throughout the
empire and herald the beginning of a new era!

Soldiers of the Prince's Imperial Army: Long live King Rex!
The rightful king! Long live! Our new king! The guarantor of
the new era! The hero who slays the wicked queen!

Soldiers of the Prince's Imperial Army: Long live King Rex!
The rightful king! Long live! The true king who sits on the
throne, the hero king of the Fotizona Empire! The hero who
slays dragons!

Prince Rex: Among those who contributed to our victory this
time, the adventurers from the Futera Guild stood out with
their remarkable achievements.

Prince Rex: The wicked Caron planned to create dragons and
rule the entire empire through fear.
Prince Rex: They are the heroes who stopped that.

Prince Rex: The name of the Dragon Slayers who saved the
empire from dragons not once, but twice, will be forever
engraved in the history of the empire!

Prince Rex: Praise the benefactors of the empire! Praise the
heroes of the empire!

Soldiers of the Prince's Imperial Army: Praise the heroes
who defeated the dragons! Hail the Dragon Slayers! Hail the
Adventurers Guild, Futera!

Soldiers of the Prince's Imperial Army: The true heroes who
saved the empire twice! Hail the Dragon Slayers! Hail the
Adventurers Guild, Futera!
Clea: Somehow, it's embarrassing, isn't it?

Mage Relm: Hehe! In times like these, you just need to stand
tall and confident!
Thief Nora: Now that I'm relieved, I'm getting hungry...

Priestess Sophia: It would be nice if they let us go
immediately... but it seems unlikely.
Clea: Once we're done here, let's all have a meal together.
Clea (I see, with this our journey...)
Clea: Now, let's go home. To our everyday lives.
Clea: To the place we should return to.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
